rows.label: tlk45450161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Whew, that was a proper struggle.
I should never have taken that
right-hand route.

rows.label: tlk45450161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, if you leave this port and head to
Baldotas Isle, the path splits in two.

rows.label: tlk45450161_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The path on the right is just teeming
with scary monsters! I'd stick to the
left path if I were you.
